Assumptions/Questions to ask:
1. User membership creation and extension
2. Searching the database of books
3. Reading a book
4. Only one active user at a time
5. Only one active book by this user 


What are the objects required?
User
Book
Library

Classes:
Library: Uses a hashtable to add and retrieve books
UserManager: Uses a hashtable to add retrieve users
Display: displays status and turns the page
User and Book: Simply hold the data for those two objects
